title: Space Shuttle Mission 2007+5.31+keygen
description:
I decided to go ahead and upload both the main installer and 5.31. I have also included the keygen. No crack or patch needed. This is my first zip please let me know if you have any issues or if it works. This should work with any update it is confirmed to work with 5.31 but once the developer finds out things might change. Make copies and save everything. Please SEED!

How to use.
1. install SSM 2007.
2. Run Game and write down hardware ID just in case.
3.Minimize game and run keygen. Your hardware ID should already be in the keygen.
4.input any serial you want.
5.click generate
6.Input serial into game. Hit enter.
7.Input reg key in to game. Hit enter.
8.install update.
9. Enjoy!
